<D>__{sir?}
<A>__{no response. alan nudges henry. no good.}
<C>__{clerk }
<D>__{sir? we need to keep the line moving. sir?}
<A>__{alan intervenes. he takes henry's copy of the novel and slides it over to benedict. benedict scribbles his name quickly and slides it back with no eye contact, yelling on the phone.}
<C>__{richard}
<P>__{(on phone)}
<D>__{absolutely not! i will sue that bastard first...}
<A>__{alan grabs the book and gives it back to henry, nudging him again.}
<C>__{alan}
<D>__{we need to move, henry.}
