<C>__{colette}
<D>__{hi there.}
<A>__{richard looks up at her for a split second and decides to ignore her. another scribbled signature as he remains on the phone. colette takes the book, trying not to look hurt. alan grabs henry and they leave the area. hannah is next up. she puts her book down on the table.}
<C>__{richard}
<P>__{(on phone)}
<D>__{damn it! that simply won't }
<A>__{richard glances up. sees hannah standing there. he stops in mid sentence. smiles.}
<C>__{richard }
<D>__{hi.}
