<D>__{hello.}
<A>__{richard hangs up the phone. the two start chatting. camera goes over to the shell shocked henry, still clutching his book, watching as hannah and richard carry on. henry is so disconcerted by what he sees that he fails to notice eudora, still with purple hair and matching glasses, the very next person in line behind hannah, waving at him.}
